channel.title: Changing worlds
channel.description:
My bot cannot change worlds. At first, I thought this had to do with the parameters you were feeding the AppletStub, but after some testing, me and nueb35 realized that wasn't it. Nueb35's bot can change worlds with no problem whatsoever, and he feeds the stub the same parameters as I do. I really do not know what is the cause of this since I thought the world changing was done in the client, not in the stub.
Can anybody explain what is wrong, and how runescape executes its world-switching?
